flowchart TD
  A[Leadership Creates Decision\n- Decision ID / branches\n- Policy thresholds\n- Trading window] --> B[Open Market Session]

  B --> C[Teams Login\n(team1...team11)]
  C --> D[Team Places Trade\nBUY branch shares]
  D --> E[Protocol Executes Trade]

  E --> F[LMSR Update\nC(q)=b*ln(sum(exp(q_i/b)))\nDelta cost = C_after - C_before]
  F --> G[Spot Probabilities Update\nP_i = exp(q_i/b)/sum(exp(q_j/b))]
  G --> H[TWAP Integrator\naccumulates P_i over time]
  H --> I[Dashboard Refresh\nSpot P + TWAP P + EV]

  I --> D

  B --> J{Window Expired?}
  J -- No --> D
  J -- Yes --> K[Close Market by TWAP Rule\nWinner = highest TWAP branch\n(spot used only as tie-break)]

  K --> L[Resolution]
  L --> M[Selected branch settles\nshares paid out normally]
  L --> N[Non-selected branch reversion\ntrade cashflows reversed]

  M --> O[Leadership Decision Output\nRECOMMEND / ESCALATE / DEFER]
  N --> O

  O --> P[Audit + Incentives\nPnL, projected balance, trade log]
